I was just talking to my gram today about how I feel like things are getting so hard on families today, mine included. Whether that's financially, medically, emotionally, spiritually, you name it. 

As I was "complaining" to her, my gram's favorite saying to tell me is "melina, don't look at the things you don't have, look at the things you DO have..." Yeah, she's wise like that! 😉🙌
And then I heard this song for the first time today.... and I think God was giving me a loving smack on the head with this song!🤔😊

If you are feeling drained by this world today, remember, we have so much to be grateful for💕 #grateful #love #family

We love all our fans, but please keep stop giving advice on things you see in an average 30 second video. 💕
